snippet: As friends, aides and donors gather for the 10th anniversary of the William J. Clinton Presidential Center, thoughts will turn to Hillary Rodham Clinton’s ambitions.
abstract: William J Clinton Presidential Center in Little Rock, Ark, is preparing to celebrate its 10th anniversary; primary focus of organizers is on Bill Clinton's accomplishments, but center is also aware of possibility of 2016 presidential campaign by Hillary Rodham Clinton.
lead_paragraph: As friends, aides and donors gather for the 10th anniversary of the William J. Clinton Presidential Center, thoughts will turn to Hillary Rodham Clinton’s ambitions.
